      "content": "i know that's what the official docs say but i'm really worried about a hypo since i'm so low right now. if i just skip it tonight, isn't that safer than risking a massive crash while i'm sleeping? it's just a tiny amount of insulin anyway, surely it won't make a huge difference for just one night?",
